N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 800.12 - Goods held for storage

State Regulations

The commission reserves the right to withhold delivery of
goods on which any terminal charges are due and unpaid at time request for
delivery is made, until such time as these charges are paid in
full. Notes
